都做主角 <br />\n<br />\n又主持埋咩正識第一大廚出馬<br />\n懶係周身刀咁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要賤格到花名都冇一個<br />\n你憎林峰可以叫佢淋瘋/ 亞太峰<br />\n你憎胡杏兒可以叫佢囧囧<br />\n你憎鄭嘉穎可以叫佢橡膠<br />\n你憎jeana可以叫佢賤娜<br />\n但憎佢呢? 只可以叫個九唔搭八既馬撚 <br />\n<br />\n最核凸果點係你呢條柒姑碌成鳩日以為自己好有料係度懷才不遇咁撚樣<br />\n要走就早走啦鬼撚留你條戇鳩仔咩<br />\n又成日以為自己好撚好戲咁教人做戲<br />\n屋企冇鏡都叫珍姐噴d西水俾你照下自己個死樣啦<br />\n<br />\n最後講多句<br />\n你條仆街馬撚咪以為依家扮晒正義撚就唔記得你當年搶撚左初哥哥既君好呀！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"老友狗狗佢做得幾好幾搞笑"},{"pid":"4b6d830c2726d2afadd5fdea688e0907618cb99c","tid":638942,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f70e6eb7f70eb2a6a50f16466abc00d58152436","tid":638942,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a1cb2f611672d610f46e398e668440a993d90ee9","tid":638942,"uid":150720,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"e83f778eaeb44cc8cc094492d131bdb05392616a","tid":638942,"uid":21423,"like":18,"dislike":86,"score":-68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"有理由懷疑肥絲大隻用程式自動回覆comment<br />\nadmin做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"肥C 好野！(食神tone)"},{"pid":"166b4857cc4d3f5ad2f37a58337e8a8cf1716e1e","tid":638942,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f70e6eb7f70eb2a6a50f16466abc00d58152436","tid":638942,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a1cb2f611672d610f46e398e668440a993d90ee9","tid":638942,"uid":150720,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"e83f778eaeb44cc8cc094492d131bdb05392616a","tid":638942,"uid":21423,"like":18,"dislike":86,"score":-68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"有理由懷疑肥絲大隻用程式自動回覆comment<br />\nadmin做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-